Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.87,0:24:20.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c159] What were you guys doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.87,0:24:18.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c85] I refuse!
