Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.72,0:24:21.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c32] Kyaa~ Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.12,0:24:22.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c195] What are we fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.38,0:24:22.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c187] It's the final song that Iwasawa left behind.
